# Kiwi Voice - Environment Variables

# ============================================
# REVENUECAT API KEY
# ============================================
# Get your API key from: https://app.revenuecat.com
# Dashboard → Project Settings → API Keys

# DEVELOPMENT (Current - Test Key)
VITE_REVENUECAT_API_KEY=test_GVsVAPHELhFcgnBFbWlVyrYGiUS

# PRODUCTION (Replace before deploying)
# VITE_REVENUECAT_API_KEY=your_production_api_key_here

# ============================================
# NEON DATABASE (PostgreSQL)
# ============================================
# Get your connection string from: https://console.neon.tech
VITE_NEON_DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:password@hostname/neondb?sslmode=require

# ============================================
# SUPABASE (Auth & Storage)
# ============================================
# Get these from: https://supabase.com → Project Settings → API
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================
# 1. Copy this file to `.env` (without .example)
# 2. The test key works for development and testing
# 3. Before deploying to production, replace with your production key
# 4. Never commit the real `.env` file to git (it's in .gitignore)
# 5. Vite env variables must start with `VITE_` to be exposed to client

# ============================================
# HOW TO GET PRODUCTION KEY
# ============================================
# 1. Go to https://app.revenuecat.com
# 2. Select your project
# 3. Click on "API Keys" in left sidebar
# 4. Copy the "Public API Key" (safe for client-side use)
# 5. Paste it above replacing the test key

# ============================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ============================================
# ✅ Public API keys are SAFE to use in client-side code
# ✅ RevenueCat validates all purchases server-side
# ✅ Private keys (secret keys) should NEVER be in client code
# ✅ This key only allows reading product info and making purchases
# ✅ Cannot be used to grant access without valid receipt
